headline: Tesla is one of the three most shorted U.S. auto stocks
summary: Investing.com -- Tesla (NASDAQ:TSLA) ranks among the three most shorted U.S. auto stocks heading into the second-quarter earnings season, alongside Rivian (NASDAQ:RIVN) and Quantumscape Corp (NYSE:QS), according to UBS.
